  "commit_message": "[CLI] Exit non-zero with a clear message when next typegen fails (#94241)\n\nThe `typegen` command chained `nextTypegen(...).then(() =>\nprocess.exit(0))` with no rejection handler. When `next.config` throws\nduring `loadConfig`, the rejection is orphaned by the synchronous\n`program.parse` and then absorbed by Next's `unhandledRejection` filter,\nso the process exits `0` having written no route types. A later `tsc`\nthen reports `Cannot find name 'PageProps'`/`'LayoutProps'` (and missing\n`*.png` modul",
